If you love hot chips, this is a great variety pack.  All of the chips in the pack are very good which includes hot cheetos, hot limon cheetos, hot funyuns, hot fries, and hot chip mix (cheetos, doritos, pretzels, spicy sunchips in one bag).  Of course these are not for you if you are on a diet, but if you want to splurge and give yourself a treat, try this variety pack.
